27
00:01:57,584 --> 00:02:00,118
Some believe
they're a bad omen.

28
00:02:00,187 --> 00:02:04,389
Tanjiro: What does that mean,
"bad omen"? How so?

29
00:02:04,391 --> 00:02:06,791
Urokodaki: Black blades
are rumored to only be wielded

30
00:02:06,861 --> 00:02:10,462
by a swordsman who has
little chance of going very far.

31
00:02:10,531 --> 00:02:12,797
( Tanjiro sighs ) Oh, well.

32
00:02:12,799 --> 00:02:16,601
I don't care
if I'm destined for greatness,

33
00:02:16,603 --> 00:02:20,605
