you'll make that happen.

36
00:02:26,146 --> 00:02:27,279
Tanjiro: Thank you.

37
00:02:27,347 --> 00:02:30,683
Urokodaki: One last thing. Here.

38
00:02:30,751 --> 00:02:35,087
A box to carry your sister
during the day,

39
00:02:35,155 --> 00:02:39,424
