called kirikumo cedar.

40
00:02:39,426 --> 00:02:43,428
It's been coated in rock lacquer
to reinforce the exterior

41
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,630
and make it even more durable.

42
00:02:45,699 --> 00:02:47,900
Tanjiro: Thanks, urokodaki.

43
00:02:47,968 --> 00:02:49,701
Oh, wow!

44
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:51,337
