grinding teeth )

167
00:12:58,112 --> 00:13:00,378
Tanjiro: There are
some things I wanna know!

168
00:13:00,447 --> 00:13:02,214
( Demon hissing,
grinding teeth )

169
00:13:04,251 --> 00:13:05,384
( Tanjiro gasps )

170
00:13:11,125 --> 00:13:13,726
- Kazumi: Who was that?
- Tanjiro: I need your help.

171
00:13:13,794 --> 00:13:16,795
Hold her for me, and stay close.

172
00:13:16,863 --> 00:13:19,765
