I can protect you!

173
00:13:23,137 --> 00:13:25,270
The ground, the wall,

174
00:13:25,339 --> 00:13:27,773
I bet it could come
from just about anywhere.

175
00:13:28,943 --> 00:13:30,342
I wouldn't be surprised

176
00:13:30,411 --> 00:13:33,045
if it could appear
out of thin air.

177
00:13:36,150 --> 00:13:40,018
Doesn't matter, because,
even if it's submerged,

178
00:13:40,087 --> 00:13:41,453
