192
00:14:28,268 --> 00:14:29,935
Tanjiro: Just one?

193
00:14:30,003 --> 00:14:32,538
Urokodaki: The first demon
there ever was.

194
00:14:32,606 --> 00:14:35,607
He's been here
for more than a thousand years.

195
00:14:35,675 --> 00:14:39,545
