all the vulnerable spots,

206
00:15:08,375 --> 00:15:10,776
because I switched forms
midway through.

207
00:15:12,980 --> 00:15:14,179
( Kazumi gasps )

208
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:22,187
Tanjiro: They all have
the same exact scent.

209
00:15:23,523 --> 00:15:25,958
Usually, demons
don't work together.

210
00:15:27,727 --> 00:15:30,996
Which means one demon
has split into three.

211
00:15:31,065 --> 00:15:33,265
I have to take them all out

212
00:15:33,333 --> 00:15:35,267
and still protect these two.

213
00:15:35,335 --> 00:15:36,534
Don't lose your nerve.

214
00:15:36,536 --> 00:15:38,336
Make him talk to you

215
00:15:38,338 --> 00:15:40,738
about muzan kibutsuji

216
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:44,176
and about how to turn a demon
back into a human!

217
00:15:46,146 --> 00:15:48,213
- Total concentration.
- ( Kazumi gasps )

218
00:15:48,282 --> 00:15:50,548
Tanjiro: Water breathing!

219
00:15:50,550 --> 00:15:54,019
Second form! Water wheel!

220
00:15:55,155 --> 00:15:57,355
( Demon groans )

221
00:15:57,357 --> 00:15:58,857
Tanjiro: Missed again.

222
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:07,966
( Grunts )

223
00:16:08,035 --> 00:16:09,234
I can't chase him,

224
00:16:09,303 --> 00:16:11,236
and I can't take a full swing

225
00:16:11,305 --> 00:16:13,439
while I'm protecting
these two, either.

226
00:16:13,507 --> 00:16:16,174
- Demon: Bastard!
- ( Tanjiro gasps )

227
00:16:16,243 --> 00:16:18,176
Demon: She'll go stale!

228
00:16:18,245 --> 00:16:21,779
Move out of the way,
you little punk!

229
00:16:21,781 --> 00:16:23,581
The girl's 16 already.

230
00:16:23,583 --> 00:16:25,651
