Take a breath, other me.

234
00:16:36,530 --> 00:16:39,731
Calm down. No big deal.

235
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:42,067
Nights like this happen, right?

236
00:16:42,136 --> 00:16:43,601
I've already feasted

237
00:16:43,603 --> 00:16:46,271
