was meaty and delicious.

239
00:16:50,277 --> 00:16:52,077
I am satisfied with that.

240
00:16:52,146 --> 00:16:55,147
Demon 1: Well, I'm not
satisfied at all, other me!

241
00:16:55,215 --> 00:16:58,616
I want to devour all of them!

242
00:16:58,686 --> 00:16:59,951
Kazumi: You monster!

243
00:17:00,020 --> 00:17:01,487
Bring satoko back,

244
00:17:01,555 --> 00:17:03,288
