249
00:17:16,236 --> 00:17:18,037
Which one was that?

250
00:17:19,239 --> 00:17:21,106
( Kazumi gasping )

251
00:17:21,175 --> 00:17:23,641
Demon 2: If her hairpin
is in this collection,

252
00:17:23,643 --> 00:17:27,513
then I'm afraid
I've already eaten her. Sorry.

